Resource Profile: Evidence Assessment ROBIS

Official URL: http://fhir.awmf.org/awmf.ig/StructureDefinition/certainty-of-evidence-rating-robis Version: 0.1.0
Draft as of 2025-08-06 Computable Name: CertaintyOfEvidenceRatingROBIS

Structured assessment of risk of bias using ROBIS (Risk of Bias in Systematic Reviews).

Guidance

This profile of a FHIR ArtifactAssessment is derived from the certainty-of-evidence-rating FHIR resource.

Usages:

  • This Profile is not used by any profiles in this Implementation Guide

You can also check for usages in the FHIR IG Statistics
